---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="3-Day Premium Free Trial | Elite Host"
  description="Start your 3-day premium web hosting free trial with Elite Host. Enjoy lightning-fast SSD storage, free SSL, cPanel management, and expert support. No credit card required!"
  keywords="free trial hosting, web hosting free trial, 3 days free trial, elite host trial, free cpanel hosting, no credit card hosting"
>
  <!-- Banner Section -->
  <div class="main-banner page-banner">
    <div class="img-up">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row g-4 align-items-center">
          <div class="col-lg-6">
            <div class="inner-content"> <span class="top-heading">3-DAYS RISK FREE</span>
              <h1>Experience Premium Hosting with Our Free Trial</h1>
              <h3>No credit card required, instant setup!</h3>
              <ul class="banner-list icon">
                <li><i class="bi bi-lightning-charge me-2"></i>Blazing Fast Performance</li>
                <li><i class="bi bi-speedometer2 me-2"></i>User Friendly Control Panel</li>
                <li><i class="bi bi-clock me-2"></i>99% Uptime Guarantee</li>
                <li><i class="bi bi-headset me-2"></i>24/7 Expert Support</li>
              </ul>
              <h4 class="mt-3"> <span>Starts at just</span> <sup>৳</sup> <strong>0</strong> <small>/3 days</small> </h4>
              <div class="inline-btns mt-3"> <a class="btns one" href="#">Get Started Now<i class="far fa-arrow-right"></i></a> </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-6">
            <div class="text-center text-lg-end"> <img src="/images/domain-img1.png" alt="Reseller Hosting"> </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Reused Solution Support Center Section -->
  <section class="section-gap">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-10 bg1 support">
          <div class="row g-4 align-items-center justify-content-between">
            <div class="col-lg-7">
              <div class="section-header">
                <h2>Our Solution Support Center</h2>
                <p>Our Solution Support Center provides expert assistance, troubleshooting, and guidance for seamless technical support.</p>
                <div class="mt-3">
                  <ul>
                    <li class="text-center"> <span class="icon"><img src="/images/talk.webp" alt=""></span>
                      <label class="content">0212 909 9656</label>
                    </li>
                    <li class="text-center"> <span class="icon"><img src="/images/support2.webp" alt=""></span>
                      <label class="content">24*7 Support</label>
                    </li>
                    <li class="text-center"> <span class="icon"><img src="/images/customer.webp" alt=""></span>
                      <label class="content">Talk to customer</label>
                    </li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4">
              <div class="text-center text-lg-end"> <img src="/images/support-center.png" alt="Reseller Hosting"> </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Reused Trial FAQs Section -->
  <section class="section-gap">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-10">
          <div class="section-header gap-bottom center">
            <h2>Free Trial Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
            <p>Got questions about our 3-day free trial? We've got answers.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-10">
          <ul class="accordion">
            <li>
              <h5>Is a credit card required to start the trial?</h5>
              <p>Absolutely not! We believe in a frictionless experience. You can sign up with just your name and email address, and your cPanel hosting account will be set up instantly.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <h5>Which features are included in the 3-day trial?</h5>
              <p>You get full, unrestricted access to cPanel, high-performance NVMe SSD storage, LiteSpeed Web Server, automated daily backups, free SSL certificates, and professional email accounts. There are no hidden feature locks.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <h5>Can I use my existing domain name for the trial?</h5>
              <p>Yes, absolutely! During the registration, you can choose to use your existing domain name. You just need to point your domain name servers (NS) to our servers to link them.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <h5>Is there any limit on support during the trial?</h5>
              <p>Not at all! Trial users receive the exact same 24/7 priority customer support as our premium paid subscribers. You can contact us via live chat or standard tickets anytime.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <h5>Is my trial website online and publicly accessible?</h5>
              <p>Yes! Your trial website is fully hosted on our live, high-speed servers. It is 100% public, secure, and ready for you to share with your customers or test your applications.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <h5>What happens after the 3 days expire?</h5>
              <p>After 3 days, your trial account will be temporarily suspended. None of your data is deleted immediately. You can upgrade to a premium paid subscription to keep your website live.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <h5>Can I keep my data if I upgrade to a paid plan?</h5>
              <p>Yes, 100%! When you upgrade to any of our paid subscription plans, all of your files, databases, configurations, and email accounts are preserved exactly as they are.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <h5>How do I upgrade from the trial to a paid plan?</h5>
              <p>Upgrading is simple. At any point during or after your trial, you can log into your billing portal and choose one of our hosting packages. Your website data remains active and completely untouched during the transition.</p>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
